com.danceUpByStas.persistence

Class GenericDao<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.danceUpByStas.persistence.GenericDao<T>

  • public class GenericDao<T>
extends java.lang.Object
    A generic DAO somewhat inspired by http://rodrigouchoa.wordpress.com This is the GenericDao class designed to store a set of generic Hibernate queries.
